For the application to work, you need to install ffmpeg.
Install the whisper, yt_dlp, pyperclip, gtts, and requests packages.
pip install yt-dlp openai-whisper requests pyperclip gtts


To turn it on:

In the clipboard, put the link to the YouTube video you want to translate.
python mp3Translate [source language] [target language]


The mp3 folder contains output.mp3, (the translated file) and source.mp3, (the source file).